"title": "5667: children, responsibilities to God",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5667",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The responsibilities of children to God as their heavenly Father include honouring and obeying him.</p>\n<h2>The responsibilities of children to their heavenly Father</h2>\n<h3>To honour and obey him in reverent fear</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps34:11\">PSA 34:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov2:5\">PRO 2:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov9:10\">PRO 9:10</a></p>\n<h3>To seek wisdom</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov4:5-Prov4:7\">PRO 4:5–4:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov1:1-Prov1:4\">PRO 1:1–1:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov8:32-Prov8:33\">PRO 8:32–8:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:1\">PRO 10:1</a></p>\n<h3>To listen and learn</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov1:8-Prov1:9\">PRO 1:8–1:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov4:1-Prov4:4\">PRO 4:1–4:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov23:22\">PRO 23:22</a></p>\n<h3>To praise God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps8:2\">PSA 8:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:15-Matt21:16\">MAT 21:15–21:16</a></p>\n<h3>To join in worship</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh12:43\">NEH 12:43</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh8:35\">JOS 8:35</a></p>\n<h2>Relationship to Jesus Christ transcends the child-parent relationship</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:29-Luke18:30\">LUK 18:29–18:30</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:29\">MAT 19:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:29-Mark10:30\">MRK 10:29–10:30</a></p>",
